snippet.title: Glum Buster - World Two - Playthrough by Ortoslon
snippet.description:
Game by CosMind: http://www.glumbuster.com/ - freeware, Windows-only, and excellent
Video by Ortoslon: http://www.youtube.com/user/ortoslon - subscribe to him and to me!

Uploaded on my account due to time length restrictions. It's very recommended that you play the game before watching these videos: use these videos only as a last resort if you get stuck.
